main event: An unidentified flying object was spotted on February 19, 1967, while shooting with a cousin.
interesting points: The UFO was described as round and white., The object was hovering at an altitude between 1800 and 1900 feet., The observers reported the incident to the nearest police., The document is part of Project Blue Book's records., The official response concluded that there was insufficient data for evaluation.
sighted object: a round and white unidentified flying object
